## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6256">Номер банковского счета Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6256">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6257">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6257">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6258">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6258">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6259">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6259">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6260">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6260">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6261">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6261">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6262">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6262">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6263">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6263">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6264">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6264">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6265">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6265">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6266">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6266">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6267">две до трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6267">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6268">Параметры дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6268">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6269">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6269">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6270">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6270">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6271">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6271">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6272">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6272">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6273">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6273">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6274">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6274">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6275">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6275">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6276">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6276">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6284">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6284">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6285">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6286">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6286">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6287">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6288">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6288">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6289">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6289">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6290">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6290">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6291">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6291">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6292">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6292">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6293">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6293">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6294">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6294">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6295">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6295">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6296">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6296">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6297">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6297">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6298">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6298">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6359">Лицензия на драйвер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6359">driver's licence#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6360">лицензии на драйвер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6360">driver's licences#</span></span>

international driving permit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6361">international driving permit</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6365">Номер дохода по некоторому контакту для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6365">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6366">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6366">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6367">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6367">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6368">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6368">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6369">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6369">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6370">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6370">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6371">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6371">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6372">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6372">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6373">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6373">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6374">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6374">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6375">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6375">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6376">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6376">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6377">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6377">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6378">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6378">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6379">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6379">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6380">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6380">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6381">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6381">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6382">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6382">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6383">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6383">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6384">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6384">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6385">ИРД но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6385">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6386">ИРД нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6386">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6387">NZ ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6387">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6388">Новая Зеландия ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6388">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6389">номер ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6389">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6390">номер дохода на землю</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6390">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6391">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6391">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6392">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6392">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6393">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6393">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6394">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6394">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6395">три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6395">three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6396">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6397">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6397">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6398">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6399">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6399">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6400">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6400">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6401">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6401">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6402">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6402">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6403">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6403">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6404">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6404">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6405">нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6405">NHI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6406">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6406">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6407">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6407">Health</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6408">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6408">treatment</span></span> 


## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6409">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6409">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6410">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6410">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6411">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6411">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6412">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6412">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6413">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6413">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6414">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6414">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6415">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6415">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6416">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6416">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6417">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6417">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6418">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6418">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6419">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6420">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6420">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6421">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6422">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6422">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6423">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6423">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6424">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6424">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6425">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6425">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6426">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6426">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6427">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6427">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6428">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6428">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6429">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6429">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6430">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6430">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6431">социальное велфаре No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6431">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6432">номер социального велфаре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6432">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6433">свн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6433">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6434">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6434">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6435">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6435">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6436">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6436">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6437">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6437">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6438">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6438">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6439">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6439">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6440">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6440">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6441">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6441">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6442">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6443">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6443">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6444">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6445">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6445">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6446">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6446">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6447">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6447">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6448">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6448">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6449">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6449">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6450">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6450">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6451">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6451">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6460">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6460">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6461">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6461">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6462">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6462">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6463">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6463">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6464">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6464">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6465">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6465">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6466">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6466">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6467">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6467">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6468">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6468">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6469">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6469">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6470">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6470">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6471">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6471">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6472">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6472">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6473">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6473">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6474">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6474">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6475">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6475">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6476">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6476">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6477">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6477">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6478">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6478">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6479">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6479">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6480">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6480">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6481">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6481">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6482">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6482">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6483">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6483">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6484">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6484">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6485">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6485">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6486">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6486">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6487">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6487">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6488">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6488">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6489">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6489">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6490">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6490">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6491">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6491">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6492">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6492">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6493">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6493">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6494">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6494">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6495">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6495">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6496">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6496">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6497">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6497">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6498">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6498">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6514">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6514">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6515">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6515">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6516">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6516">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6517">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6517">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6518">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6518">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6519">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6519">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6520">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6520">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6521">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6521">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6522">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6522">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6523">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6523">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6524">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6524">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6525">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6525">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6526">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6526">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6527">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6527">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6528">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6528">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6529">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6529">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6530">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6530">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6531">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6531">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6532">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6532">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6533">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6533">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6534">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6534">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6535">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6535">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6536">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6536">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6537">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации страны ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6537">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6538">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6538">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6539">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6539">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6540">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6540">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6541">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6541">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6542">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6542">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6543">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6543">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6544">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6544">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6545">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6545">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6546">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6546">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6547">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6547">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6548">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6548">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->      
<Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6549">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6549">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6550">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6550">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6551">довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6551">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6552">довóдособисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6552">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6553">ниеповтарзални нумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6553">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6554">ниеповтарзалнинумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6554">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6560">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6560">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6561">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6561">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6562">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6562">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6563">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6563">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6564">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6564">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6565">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6565">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6566">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6566">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6567">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6567">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6568">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6568">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6569">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6569">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6570">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6570">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6571">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6571">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6572">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6572">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6575">Нумер пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6575">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6576">НР.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6576">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6577">пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6577">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6578">пасзпорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6578">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6579">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6579">Poland REGON number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6580">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6580">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6581">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6581">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6582">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6582">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6583">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6583">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6584">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6584">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6585">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6585">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6586">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6586">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6587">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6587">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6588">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6588">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6589">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6589">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6590">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6590">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6591">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6591">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6592">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6592">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6593">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6593">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6594">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6594">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6595">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6595">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6612">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6612">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6613">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6613">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6614">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6614">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6615">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6615">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6616">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6616">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6617">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6617">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6618">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6618">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6619">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6619">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6620">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6620">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6621">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6621">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6622">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6622">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6623">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6623">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6624">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6624">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6625">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6625">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6655">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6655">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6656">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации страны ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6656">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6657">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в номер социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентный тип конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6657">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6658">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6659">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6659">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6660">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6661">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6661">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6662">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6662">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6663">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6663">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6664">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6664">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6665">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6665">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6666">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6666">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6667">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6667">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6687">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6687">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6688">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6688">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6689">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6689">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6690">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь чисел в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6690">two letters followed by a seven numbers in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6691">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6691">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6692">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6692">two letters followed by seven numbers with special characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6693">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6693">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6694">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6694">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6695">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6695">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6696">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6696">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6697">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6697">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6698">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6698">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6699">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6699">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6700">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6700">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6701">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6701">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6702">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6702">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6703">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6703">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6709">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6709">driver licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6716">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6716">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6719">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6719">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6720">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6720">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6721">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6721">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6722">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6722">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6723">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6723">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6724">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6724">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6725">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6725">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6726">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6726">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6727">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6728">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6728">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6729">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6730">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6730">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6731">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6731">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6732">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6732">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6733">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6733">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6734">Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6734">Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6735">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6735">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6736">номер паспорта для португальского языка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6736">portuguese passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6737">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6737">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6738">нúмеро Do пассапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6738">número do passaporte</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6739">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6739">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6740">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6740">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6741">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6741">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6742">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6742">nine digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6743">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6743">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6744">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6744">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6745">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6746">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6746">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6747">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6748">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6748">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6749">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6749">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6750">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6750">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6751">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6751">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6752">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6752">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6777">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6777">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6778">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6778">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6779">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6779">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6780">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6780">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6781">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6781">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6782">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6782">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6783">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6783">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6784">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6784">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6785">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6785">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6786">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6786">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6787">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6787">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6788">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6788">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6789">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6789">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6790">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6790">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6806">Национальный идентификационный номер Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6806">Romania national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6807">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации ЕС по национальному идентификационному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6807">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6808">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6808">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6809">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6809">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6810">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6810">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6811">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6811">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6812">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6812">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6813">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6813">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6814">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6814">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6815">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6815">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6816">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6816">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6817">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6817">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6818">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6818">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-6819">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-6819">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!--Romania national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
