- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7924">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7924">身份證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7925">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7925">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7926">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7926">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7927">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7927">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7928">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7928">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7929">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7929">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7930">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7930">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7931">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7931">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7932">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7932">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7933">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7933">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7934">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7934">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7935">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7935">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7936">Номер паспорта для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7936">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7937">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7937">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7938">номер биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7938">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7939">номер биометрической службы Passport: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7939">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7940">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7940">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7941">номер биометрического паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7941">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7942">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7942">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7943">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7943">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7944">номер биометрической службы Passport:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7944">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7945">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7945">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7946">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7946">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7947">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7947">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7948">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7948">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7949">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7949">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7950">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7950">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7951">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7951">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7952">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7952">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7953">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7953">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7954">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7954">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7955">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7955">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7956">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7956">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7957">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7957">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7958">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7958">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7959">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7959">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7960">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7960">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7961">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7961">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7962">Номер сертификата резидента (ARC/TARC) для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7962">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7963">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7963">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7964">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7964">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7965">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7965">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7966">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7966">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7967">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7967">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7968">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7968">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7969">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7969">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7970">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7970">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7971">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7971">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7972">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7972">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7973">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7973">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7974">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7974">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7975">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7975">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7976">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7976">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7977">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7977">Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7978">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7978">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7979">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7979">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7980">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7980">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7981">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7981">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7982">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7982">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7983">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7983">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7984">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7984">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7985">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7985">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7986">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7986">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7987">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7987">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7988">Код идентификации для тайского заполнения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7988">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7989">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7989">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7990">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7990">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7991">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7991">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7992">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7992">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7993">Первая цифра не равна нулю или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7993">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7994">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7994">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7995">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7995">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7996">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7996">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7997">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7997">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7998">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7998">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-7999">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-7999">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8000">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8000">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8001">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8001">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8002">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8002">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8003">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8003">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8004">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8004">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8005">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8005">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8006">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8006">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8007">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8007">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8008">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8008">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8009">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8009">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8010">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8010">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8011">Турецкий национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8011">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8012">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8012">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8013">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8013">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8014">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8014">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8015">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8015">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8016">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8016">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8017">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8017">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8018">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8018">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8019">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8019">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8020">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8020">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8021">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8021">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8022">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8022">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8023">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8023">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8024">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8024">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8025">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8025">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8026">TC Кимлик No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8026">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8027">TC Кимлик нумарасı</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8027">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8028">Ватандаşлıк нумарасı</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8028">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8029">Ватандаşлıк нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8029">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8030">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8030">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8031">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8031">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8032">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8032">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8033">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8033">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8034">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8034">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8035">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8035">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8036">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8036">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8037">пять букв (без учета регистра) или цифра 9 вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8037">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8038">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8038">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8039">пять цифр в формате даты ММДДИ для даты рождения (седьмой символ увеличивается на 50, если драйвер — гнездо, то есть 51 – 62, а не с 01 – 12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8039">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8040">две буквы (без учета регистра) или цифра "9" вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8040">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8041">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8041">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8042">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8042">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8043">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8043">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8044">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8044">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8045">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8045">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8046">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8046">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8047">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8047">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8048">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8048">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8049">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8049">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_drivers_license"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8050">Keyword_uk_drivers_license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8050">Keyword_uk_drivers_license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8051">двла</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8051">DVLA</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8052">light vans</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8052">light vans</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8053">куадбикес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8053">quadbikes</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8054">motor cars</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8054">motor cars</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8055">125cc</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8055">125cc</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8056">сидекар</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8056">sidecar</span></span>

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8066">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8066">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8067">номер рулона електорал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8067">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8068">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8068">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8069">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1-4 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8069">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8070">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8070">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8071">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют 1-4 номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8071">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8072">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8072">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8073">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8073">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8074">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8074">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8075">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8075">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8076">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8076">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8077">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8077">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8078">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8078">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8079">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8079">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8084">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8084">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8085">Национальный номер службы работоспособности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8085">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8086">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8086">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8087">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8087">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8088">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8088">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8089">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8089">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8090">либо три, либо десять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8090">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8091">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8091">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8092">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8092">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8093">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8093">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8094">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8094">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8095">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8095">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8096">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8096">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8097">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8097">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8098">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8098">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8099">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8099">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8100">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8100">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8101">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8101">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8102">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8102">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8103">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8103">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8104">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8104">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8122">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8122">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8123">Национальный страховой номер (Нино)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8123">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8124">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной конфиденциальной информации ЕС Идентификаитон и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8124">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8125">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8125">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8126">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8126">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8127">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8127">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8128">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8128">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8129">две буквы (допустимые Нинос используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, которые пропускаются при проверке этого шаблона; без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8129">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8130">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8130">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8131">"A", "B", "C", или "'D" (например, префикс, в суффиксе допускаются только определенные символы; без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8131">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8132">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8132">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8133">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8133">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8134">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8134">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8135">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8135">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8136">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8136">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8137">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8137">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8138">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8138">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8139">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8139">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8140">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8140">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8141">значение "A", "B", "C" или "'D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8141">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8142">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8142">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8143">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8143">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8144">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8144">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8145">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8145">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8146">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8146">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8147">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8147">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8148">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8148">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8149">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8149">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8150">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8150">No keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NINO -->
<Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8151">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8151">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8152">Keyword_uk_nino</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8152">Keyword_uk_nino</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8153">national insurance number
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8153">national insurance number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8154">national insurance contributions
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8154">national insurance contributions</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8155">protection act</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8155">protection act</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8156">страхования</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8156">insurance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8157">social security number
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8157">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8158">insurance application
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8158">insurance application</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8159">medical application
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8159">medical application</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8160">social insurance
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8160">social insurance</span></span>

## <a name="uk-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8172">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8172">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8173">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8173">tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8174">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации по идентификационному номеру Европейского налога ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8174">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8175">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8175">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8176">Уникальная справочная информация о налогоплательщиках (утр): 10 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8176">unique Taxpayer Reference (UTR): 10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8177">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8177">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8178">Уникальная справочная информация о налогоплательщиках (утр): 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8178">unique Taxpayer Reference (UTR): 10 digits</span></span>

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8179">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8179">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8180">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8180">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8181">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8181">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8182">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8182">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8183">Функция  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8183">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8184">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8184">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8204">Номер банковского счета США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8204">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8205">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8205">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8206">8-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8206">8-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8207">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8207">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8208">8–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8208">8-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8209">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8209">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8210">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8210">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8211">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8211">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8212">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8212">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8213">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8213">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8214">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8214">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8244">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8244">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8245">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8245">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8246">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8246">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8247">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8247">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8248">зависит от штата — например, Нью Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8248">depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8249">девять цифр, отформатированных как DDD DDD DDD, будут совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8249">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8250">девять цифр, такие как ццццццццц, не совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8250">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8251">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8251">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8252">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8252">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8253">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8253">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8254">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8254">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8255">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8255">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8256">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8256">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8257">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8257">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8258">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8258">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8259">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8259">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8260">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8260">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8261">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8261">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8262">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8262">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8263">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8263">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8264">Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8264">Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8265">DL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8265">DL</span></span>

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8360">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (SHAREPOINTВ) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8360">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8361">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8361">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8362">девять цифр, начинающиеся с цифры "9" и содержащие "7" или "8" в качестве четвертой цифры, при необходимости отформатированные с помощью пробелов или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8362">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8363">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8363">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8364">форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8364">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8365">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8365">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8366">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8366">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8367">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8367">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8368">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8368">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8369">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8369">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8370">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8370">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8371">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8371">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8372">неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8372">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8373">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8373">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8374">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8374">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8375">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8375">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8376">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8376">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8377">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8377">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8378">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8378">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8379">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8379">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8380">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8380">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8381">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8381">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8382">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8382">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8383">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8383">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8384">функция Func_us_address находит адрес в правильном формате;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8384">The function Func_us_address finds an address in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8385">функция Func_us_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8385">The function Func_us_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8386">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin_collaborative.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8386">A keyword from Keyword_itin_collaborative is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8387">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8387">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8388">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8388">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8389">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8389">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8390">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8390">A keyword from Keyword_itin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8391">функция Func_us_address находит адрес в правильном формате;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8391">The function Func_us_address finds an address in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8392">функция Func_us_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8392">The function Func_us_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
<Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_address" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_date" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin_collaborative" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_address" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_date" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8413">Номер социального страхования (SSN) США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8413">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8414">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8414">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8415">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8415">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8416">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8416">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8417">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8417">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8418">четыре функции ищут служб SSNs в четырех различных шаблонах:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8418">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8419">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8419">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8420">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8420">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8421">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8421">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8422">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8422">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8423">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8424">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8424">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8425">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8426">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8426">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8427">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8427">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8428">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8428">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8429">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8429">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8430">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8430">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8431">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8431">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8432">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8432">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8433">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8433">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8434">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8434">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8435">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 55 % верно обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах ближайших 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8435">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8436">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8436">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8437">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8437">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8438">Keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8438">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8452">США/ВЕЛИКОБРИТАНИЯ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8452">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8453">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8453">passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8454">Великобритания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8454">The U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8455">Объект типа конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8455">passport number sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8456">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8456">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8457">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8457">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8458">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8458">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8459">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8459">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8460">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8460">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8461">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8461">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8462">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8462">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8463">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8463">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8464">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8464">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8465">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8465">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8486">Украина Passport Россия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8486">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8487">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8487">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8488">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8488">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8489">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8489">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8490">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8490">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8491">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8491">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8492">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8492">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8493">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8493">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8494">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8494">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8495">Регулярное выражение Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8495">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8496">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8496">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8505">Украина Passport International</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8505">Ukraine passport international</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8506">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8507">буквенно-цифровой шаблон из восьми символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8507">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8508">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8509">8-значный буквенно-цифровой шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8509">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8510">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8510">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8511">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8511">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8512">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8512">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8513">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8513">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8514">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8514">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8515">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8515">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8516">Регулярное выражение Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8516">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="be1bb-8517">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be1bb-8517">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
